		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That guide is badly outdated, since it uses Nesticle and a bunch of DOS tools.
<br />
<br />The process is actually a bit more complex than that, since I haven't read anything about compression in this guide, and most RPGs and other games with large volumes of text do use compression.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
